sequenceDiagram
    participant PlatformOp as Platform Operator<br/>(rhods-operator)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as MLflow Operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant Helm as Helm Renderer<br/>(in-process)
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (service-ca)
    participant InitCA as combine-ca-bundles<br/>(init container)
    participant InitMig as db-migration<br/>(init container)
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>9000/TCP HTTPS

    Note over PlatformOp,S3: Flow 1: MLflow CR Reconciliation

    PlatformOp->>K8sAPI: Create MLflow CR (cluster-scoped, singleton)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (MLflow CR created/updated)
    Operator->>Helm: Render charts/mlflow with CR spec values
    Helm-->>Operator: Unstructured Kubernetes objects
    Note over Operator: Post-render: inject db-migration<br/>init container (migration.go)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply (Deployment, Service,<br/>NetworkPolicy, PVC, RBAC, ServiceMonitor)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update HTTPRoute<br/>(parentRef: data-science-gateway)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ConsoleLink<br/>(OpenShift console menu)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update MLflow CR status<br/>(URLs, conditions)

    Note over PlatformOp,S3: Flow 2: Pod Startup (CA Bundle + Migration)

    K8sAPI-->>InitCA: Pod scheduled, init containers start
    InitCA->>InitCA: Read system CA (/etc/pki/tls/certs/ca-bundle.crt)
    InitCA->>InitCA: Read platform CA (odh-trusted-ca-bundle ConfigMap)
    InitCA->>InitCA: Read custom CA (optional ConfigMap)
    InitCA->>InitCA: Write combined CA to emptyDir volume
    InitCA-->>InitMig: Init container complete
    InitMig->>PG: Connect (TLS verify-full)<br/>Connection string credentials
    InitMig->>InitMig: mlflow db fix-migration-gap<br/>(Alembic schema migration)
    InitMig-->>MLflow: Init container complete, server starts

    Note over PlatformOp,S3: Flow 3: External Client Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/...<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>Token passthrough
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>(user's token, mlflow.kubeflow.org resources)
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Allowed/Denied
    alt Authorized
        MLflow->>PG: Query metadata<br/>TLS verify-full, connection string creds
        PG-->>MLflow: Metadata results
        MLflow->>S3: Get/Put artifacts<br/>HTTPS, AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>MLflow: Artifact data
        MLflow-->>Gateway: JSON Response (200 OK)
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
    else Denied
        MLflow-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
        Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Note over PlatformOp,S3: Flow 4: CA Bundle Watcher (continuous)

    loop Every 30 seconds
        Note over MLflow: ca-bundle-watcher sidecar
        MLflow->>MLflow: Poll source CA files for changes
        alt CA files changed
            MLflow->>MLflow: Regenerate combined CA bundle
        end
    end
